# Frontend conventions

## Structure

- Use the App Router (`src/app/`), not the Pages Router
- Server Components by default; add `"use client"` only when needed (hooks, browser APIs, event handlers)
- Colocate route-specific code under `src/app/`; shared UI under `src/components/` when it grows

## Styling

- Use Tailwind utility classes; follow patterns in `src/app/page.tsx` and `src/app/globals.css`
- Support light and dark mode where the rest of the page does

## Components

- Use TypeScript with explicit props types
- Prefer named exports for reusable components
- Use `next/image` for images and `next/link` for internal navigation

## Reference

- Default home page: @src/app/page.tsx
- Root layout: @src/app/layout.tsx
